FBIS4-36425 "drnes111_j_94029" FBIS-NES-94-111 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen South Reports Air Raids on Little Aden, Injuries South Reports Air Raids on Little Aden, Injuries EA0806163094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 8 Jun 94 EA0806163094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 8 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpt] The Air Force of the al-Ahmar gang today made three air raids on the city of Little Aden [west of Aden] targeting the residential quarters of the peaceful citizens. Our air defenses succeeded in shooting at least one aircraft down, prompting the rest to flee. As a result of this indiscriminate attack on the town, a number of children were seriously injured and they have been taken to the hospital. [passage omitted]
